  <section class="services">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Terms of Service</h2>
        <p>These terms govern your use of LuxeDrive’s services. By booking a vehicle, you agree to comply with these terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i></div>
          <h3>Agreement</h3>
          <p>By renting a vehicle, you enter into a legal agreement with LuxeDrive and agree to follow all applicable laws and these terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i></div>
          <h3>Eligibility</h3>
          <p>Renters must be at least 18 years old, hold a valid driver’s license, and meet LuxeDrive’s driving history requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-car-side"></i></div>
          <h3>Vehicle Use</h3>
          <p>Vehicles must be used for lawful purposes only. Off-road use, racing, and sub-renting are strictly prohibited.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-gas-pump"></i></div>
          <h3>Fuel Policy</h3>
          <p>Vehicles must be returned with the same fuel level as at pickup. Additional charges apply for refueling.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i></div>
          <h3>Rental Duration</h3>
          <p>Rental periods begin at vehicle pickup and end when the vehicle is returned. Late returns may incur fees.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i></div>
          <h3>Payments & Deposits</h3>
          <p>All bookings require full payment in advance. Security deposits may apply depending on the vehicle category.</p>
        </div>

       <div class="service-card">
           <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i></div>
           <h3>Documents</h3>
           <p>All renters must present valid identification and legal driving documents, including a government-issued photo ID and a valid driver’s license.</p>
       </div>


        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i></div>
          <h3>Liability</h3>
          <p>Renters are responsible for any damages, traffic fines, or legal violations during the rental period.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-ban"></i></div>
          <h3>Termination</h3>
          <p>LuxeDrive reserves the right to terminate rentals without refund in case of contract violations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
